Hello {0}

I hope you are doing well !

The test period for {1} is coming to an end. This means that we will no longer check your quality indicators and customer complaints every week.
However, we would like to remind you that the quality of your products as well as the quality of customer complaint management remains crucial to your success in the Back Market.
Also, we advise you to put as many ads online as possible with stock to ensure you sell well on our platform. We remain available by email if you have any questions about your Back Office, your announcements, your customer complaints or even your quality indicators.
It is a pleasure to have you as a Back Market reseller!
See you soon,
The Back Market Team
